## Advanced Configuration

### Automerge

Auto-merge PR when all specified images are updated:

```yaml
with:
  automerge-images: app-backend,app-frontend,app-worker
```

### Custom Applications Directory

```yaml
with:
  applications-directory: manifests/apps
```

